snippet.title: DRAGON BALL FighterZ - Gogeta [SSGSS] Character Trailer | X1, PS4, PC, Switch
snippet.description:
A powerful fusion warrior is reborn! SSGSS Gogeta is arriving to #DRAGONBALLFighterZ as part of the FighterZ Pass 2!

Are you ready to add this mighty warrior to your team? Order today: https://bandainam.co/DBFZ
